scenes.description: Title card and introduction sequence featuring guest members Nekomata Okayu, Shirogane Noel, Houshou Marine, Usada Pekora, Tokoyami Towa, Shishiro Botan, Sakamata Chloe, and Mori Calliope.
Countdown sequence from 10 to 1 leading to the start of the live performance.
Takane Lui appears on stage and begins her first song, "Overload".

subtitles.original: 市ノ宮 渋滞 帰りの会で
subtitles.english: Ichinomiya, traffic jam, at the end-of-day meeting

subtitles.original: 面倒くさそう 押しつけられてる
subtitles.english: Looking annoyed, having things pushed onto me

subtitles.original: なにもからなにもまで
subtitles.english: From this to that, everything

subtitles.original: 死語 相槌 まとめ役なら
subtitles.english: Dead words, backchanneling, if I'm the mediator

subtitles.original: 聞き上手 上手にうなずき合ってる
subtitles.english: A good listener, nodding along skillfully

subtitles.original: 仲良しこよしで
subtitles.english: Playing nice and friendly

subtitles.original: さあ ダダダ 溜まり 溜まり 貯めよ
subtitles.english: Now, da-da-da, let it pile up, pile up, save it up

subtitles.original: 言えないね そんな 強い言葉は
subtitles.english: Can't say them, such strong words

subtitles.original: 少しだけ 静かにしてほしいね
subtitles.english: I'd like it to be just a little bit quieter

subtitles.original: あぁ 私たち 待望へ
subtitles.english: Ah, towards our long-awaited goal

subtitles.original: 世界 テテテ 降伏やいや
subtitles.english: World, te-te-te, surrender, no no

subtitles.original: 果たせ その日まで
subtitles.english: Carry it out, until that day

subtitles.original: ネネネ 降伏やいや
subtitles.english: Ne-ne-ne, surrender, no no

subtitles.original: あなたの周りも ヨヨヨ
subtitles.english: Around you too, yo-yo-yo

subtitles.original: 警戒 セセセ 降伏あれあらあ
subtitles.english: Caution, se-se-se, surrender, oh my oh my

subtitles.original: 約束の地まで
subtitles.english: Until the promised land

subtitles.original: さあ 掲げよう バッテン バッテン
subtitles.english: Now, let's raise it, X mark, X mark

subtitles.original: デンデン 降伏やいや
subtitles.english: Den-den, surrender, no no

subtitles.original: 今日も 嫌い そっちのけだね
subtitles.english: Hating it today too, putting it aside

subtitles.original: 嫌になるから 私一人でも
subtitles.english: Because I'm getting sick of it, even if I'm alone

subtitles.original: やっていくわ
subtitles.english: I'll keep going
